dmca.title: Blogger DMCA Complaint- Richard van der Woelling
dmca.body:
Ladies and Gentlemen:
 
Please immediately remove or disable all access to the following Infringing Material.
 
The copyrighted work at issue is the image that appears on: http://winandwin228.blogspot.com/2006/12/hong-kong-tai-o.html
 
The original work appears here: http://http://www.hongkongphotographic.com/2006/11/creekside_dawn.php
 
The copyrighted work at issue is the image that appears on: http://winandwin228.blogspot.com/2006/12/hong-kong-botanical-gardens.html
 
The original work appears here: http://www.bigwhiteguy.com/photos/photo.php?imageID=1691
